text: Vaceuchelus vangoethemi is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Chilodontaidae. ==Original description== * Poppe G.T., Tagaro S.P. & Dekker H. (2006) The Seguenziidae, Chilodontidae, Trochidae, Calliostomatidae and Solariellidae of the Philippine Islands. Visaya Supplement 2: 1–228. ==References== vangoethemi Category:Gastropods described in 2006
